Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, be careful and don't get carried away, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, the water is all salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's salt water, Ritchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, there're waves here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there're waves, Ritchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hey're not listening to a word I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura High Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did forget how to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma used to compliment me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yui," she said, "as soon as you learn one thing, everything else seems to leave your head."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that was a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Summer vacation is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the beach?! Or maybe to the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going out there to play around! This will be a band training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be practicing nonstop from sunup to sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better buy new clothes to wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I need to buy a swimsuit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon after the end of summer vacation is the high school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,High school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! In the past, the Light Music Club was pretty famous for its incredible live performances at the Sakura High Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That festival is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,School festivals at high schools are pretty elaborate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Concession!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I really wanna have a full-on maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A haunted house would be a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a maid café is the way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you only whacked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Light Music Club, aren't we? We are performing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone. Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some madeleines?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think, Mugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know at the beginning, I said we should take things slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I mean, come on, it's been three months now. We haven't played together a single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now, now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Six times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of having a sleepover with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, should we go out to the beach? Or how about--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, this is going to be a training camp for the band!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is this training camp going to cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she's right. We're on a tight budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a summer house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.92,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Of course she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How about getting out of bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And aren't those my pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A little longer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine morning to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I can't believe I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and after we warned you not to oversleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I was way too excited to get a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a grade-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, seems she's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she did say this was her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The gel type will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder what she's dreaming about right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think we need to get a picture of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, that'd be really mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for our memory album!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you woke her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now that you're awake, you really gotta tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this cool summer home of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.98,Alternative,,0,0,0,,and hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Smell that salty air!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Swimming, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, we didn't come here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I had hoped to stay in one of our larger vacation houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, I only got permission to borrow our smallest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your smallest house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all this space!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that they didn't need to leave anything out for us, but I guess they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugi, what's in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a princess bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I always tell them that I'd like things to be as normal as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They just don't seem to understand what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been used recently, so I'm worried that the gear might not work properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everything looks okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are Yui and Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. They wandered off at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a past Light Music Club playing at the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it in the clubroom earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're way, way better than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard this, it's like I had this sudden urge not to be outdone by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is that why you suggested this training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugi—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Time to have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fast! What about practice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go on ahead, so you two hurry up and get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You still sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mio, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you mean you're gonna go with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We may as well enjoy ourselves a little while we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought we'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugi, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll all be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me! I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two weeks since we tragically washed ashore on this desert island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, although I thought we were done for when we were cast adrift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you gotta admit this is kind of fun in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a grand find...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight we feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of crazy scenario are you acting out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yui! Let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure is a pretty place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell me, what did you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It just grew to this size before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared, I'm not scared, I'm not scared, I'm not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.17,Alternative,,0,0,0,,When you go to the doctor, your kneecaps will be covered with corn barnacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I swallowed seawater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it at last to the golden island of Zipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The day's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here at the beach and all, it's a beautiful day and if we don't live it up, what was the point of coming all this way and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You forgot about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault, Ritsu, with your going on and on about goofing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, well, which of us do you think was having the most fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so stuffed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor feels wonderfully nice and cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you close your eyes, it almost feels like you're being carried far away out to sea by the ocean waves, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're right, it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Ritchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, guys. We're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get up, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mugi, stand back for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, can we just call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to practice and so that's what we're gonna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we're tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask, have you been putting on a bit weight lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially around your mid-section.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because you haven't been playing the drums lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This guitar feels like it weighs a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you before you bought it that you should get a lighter one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that told me to buy this guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor's warmed up, it's not as comfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll, roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, you'll get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This spot's nice and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you expect to play in the school festival if we don't practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, I told you that we should do a maid café.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think we should do a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, you're not following me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely at Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this got to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face it, Mio. There aren't many people in this world better suited to the maid look than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:57.76,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Black stockings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A lily-white apron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And a maid headband!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The adorable power of cute compels you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'd have a catch phrase like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Squad Member Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're done with this, we're really gonna start practicing, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We know, we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.26,Alternative,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for our last number!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, it's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Budget issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're gonna be going off like crazy at our Budokan show, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Budokan show?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's what we all settle down on as our goal, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I want the fireworks to be pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a grade-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it'd be cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd look like a bunch of kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think pink would be a little much, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If all we're going to do is try to play at the Budokan, then we need to get at least as good as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I think I could play this song...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you people to arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape must have switched over to side B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not listening, I'm not listening, I'm not listening, I'm not listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.05,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Scary ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In a scary haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No more... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Mio. Everything's okay, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a ghost on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.83,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of cute compels you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yui, did you really mean what you said about that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There! How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but not quite. I don't know how to make it go "myon".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Myon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I think you must be talking about choking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This choking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Choking is when you pull on the strings to bend them and change the sound while a note is being played.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a spook afraid of ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you even have an outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly had a lot of fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you were right, Mugi. Maybe I should just try to relax a bit and not worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should've had a lot more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your bangs are long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're long, but surprisingly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks! Wait a second, what do you mean by "surprisingly"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're trying for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you can tell? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all you need to is stick out your ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Music is a wonderful thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun playing music together with everybody for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would've missed out on it if you hadn't suggested having a training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Mio's all embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not! I'm red from the heat and that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, all right?! So, just drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, Mio's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... Come back here, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you said the pictures from the training camp are ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That one turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have that shot of--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the negatives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a digital camera, there's no negatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mio! We're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hang on! I'll just be a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I don't see it listed anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.51,0:23:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. You kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamanaka, did you used to play the guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but some friends of mine did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in a cardboard box you found the other day, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like pictures of an old Light Music Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! I knew you can do it, Nodoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Advisor?
